listings.comment: Definitely went above and beyond in delivering high quality work. Called me 2x via zoom and delivered an as-expected site on webflow, ready to be published and used. Bravo. Will tap again.

I hate to write this review because I would want to keep this persons work for myself! Malcom did what we wanted for https://www.pulsesolar.com and then some. His pricing is very fair. We are scheduling more work with Malcom ASAP to continue adding more functionality to the site. 5 stars +

Malcolm was an absolute pleasure to work with! He responded quickly to all my messages and completed every task on my website exactly as I had envisioned. His attention to detail and dedication to getting everything just right really stood out.

He even went above and beyond by suggesting additional improvements that made the final result even better than I expected. Highly professional, efficient, and skilled—I'll definitely be returning for future projects. Highly recommend!

This is probably the 20th time I've worked with Malcom - he's a super self starter and brilliant worker - always gets the job done in the time you need and highly skilled on everything tech! 

Would really recommend him for all things webflow, zapier and many others

I had an amazing experience working with this Malcom! They went above and beyond to help me bring my vision to life. Not only were they highly skilled and professional, but they were also incredibly patient and communicative throughout the entire process. Their attention to detail and ability to troubleshoot complex issues made a huge difference in the final outcome. My website looks stunning, functions perfectly, and is exactly what I was hoping for. I highly recommend their services to anyone looking for a top-notch Webflow expert!
